title: Sports: Manchester United's Michael Carrick for shock move to Arsenal
text:
By Game Yetu Sunday, February 5th 2017 at 14:55 [PHOTO: COURTESY] 
Arsenal lead the quest for Manchester United playmaker Michael Carrick after Jose Mourinho refused to give assurances on his future at Manchester United. 
The Manchester United midfielderâ€™s contract is set to expire at the end of the season and Arsene Wenger is ready to pounce on a stunning free transfer deal. 
Michael Carrick who has been a key performer for Manchester United this season is said to have suffered for the better part of this season as Mourinho has not been giving him regular starts.
